) Three intragastrically injected mice of the indicated groups were sacrificed at the indicated day after inoculation; intestine homogenates were applied for the quantification of viral load by RT-qPCR. The gray and black bars represent the viral loads of the mice pretreated with pantoprazole and mock-treated with PBS, respectively. Data are means and SD of three mice.

